{"tid":2234661,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"被釘牌教師首發聲謝市民關心支持 澄清毋須找上門補習工作","createTime":"2020-10-08T05:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T15:10:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f93de1076ab6fcb6df5940af3632a139174a327f","tid":2234661,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:13:30.000Z","msg":"九龍塘宣道小學一名教師被教育局指「有計劃地散播港獨訊息」而釘牌。該名教師透過教協傳達訊息，感謝市民的關心和支持，惟澄清自己毋須如網上流傳指需尋找上門補習的工作。<br />\n<br />\n教協於Facebook專頁發帖，表示一直跟進和支援被除牌教師個案，有見於近日網上有傳教師「急需尋找上門補習工作」，該教師希望透過教協傳達訊息：「感謝各位的關心和支持，但現時我並無需要尋找上門補習的工作，謝謝大家！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/UXZRPPCRNBBQNEKEPBIMMHQOII/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FUXZRPPCRNBBQNEKEPBIMMHQOII%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5LM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=8c2a705b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FUXZRPPCRNBBQNEKEPBIMMHQOII%2F&h=9dcd6489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/UXZRPPCRNBBQNEKEPBIMMHQOII/</a>"},{"pid":"540baa70b7e1097f60d01d58b7acbc28de19d32b","tid":2234661,"uid":354682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bcdddb9c145eac35475f6bbed5ad44f3658f74","tid":2234661,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"540baa70b7e1097f60d01d58b7acbc28de19d32b","tid":2234661,"uid":354682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=